  <h3 class=" unit-title text-center">Intro</h3><br>
  <p>
  Risk: World War 1 is a total conversion mod for Starcraft 2, where the map consists of Europe and North Africa. Each player chooses from 9 possible nations, and fights with their allies to conquer land and win the war. Teams are based upon which nation you chose and cannot be changed.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>The Entente:</strong> France (blue), Russia (purple), Britain (red), Italy (green), and Serbia (brown)</li>
    <li><strong>The Central Powers:</strong> Germany (black), Austria (pink), Bulgaria (orange), and the Ottomans (yellow)</li>
  </ul>
